{"type": "article", "id": 31957, "title": "UA大力扩展女性产品线，以及，Missoni 版的匡威非常不错 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-08T02:34:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12630, "name": "中国经济"}, {"id": 14105, "name": "porter"}, {"id": 26100, "name": "2020 东京奥运会"}, {"id": 32555, "name": "意大利时尚产业"}, {"id": 795, "name": "Air Jordan"}, {"id": 2145, "name": "Converse"}, {"id": 2634, "name": "Under Armour"}, {"id": 3154, "name": "Levi’s"}, {"id": 9942, "name": "Elizabeth Arden"}, {"id": 10635, "name": "Visvim"}, {"id": 22261, "name": "Revlon"}, {"id": 5146, "name": "周杰伦"}, {"id": 9021, "name": "余文乐"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/201609072307375cOte9CmiZXkHhjv.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/mergers-acquisitions/revlon-completed-elizabeth-arden-acquisition-fragrance-beauty-10524297/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Revlon 完成了对 Elizabeth Arden 的收购</b></a> | 今年六月，Revlon 宣布以 8.7 亿美元的价格收购同行 Elizabeth Arden。日前，Revlon 完成了这项交易。Elizabeth Arden 的股票将不再出现在美国纳斯达克。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/under-armour-womens-footwear-10524141/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Under Armour 将大力扩展女士产品线</b></a> | Under Armour 的财务总监  Chip Molloy 对投资者称，该公司将大力扩展女士产品线，在 2017 年的春夏季，将有更多的新产品问世。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/forecasts-analysis/italy-fashion-industry-grows-10523161/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>意大利时尚产业预计今年上涨 1.4%</b></a> | 意大利时尚商会的时尚经济趋势报告指出，意大利的时尚产业在 2016 年预计实现 864 亿欧元的营收，同比上涨 1.4%。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/denim/david-love-named-president-levis-strauss-asia-middle-east-and-africa-10523902/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Levi’s 集团任命新的亚洲、中东、非洲地区首席执行官</b></a> | David Love 将成为 Levi’s 在亚洲、中东、非洲地区的首席执行官。他将负责领导公司在这些地区的贸易运转，扩宽品牌渠道。他此前曾担任 Levi’s 集团的全球供应链副总裁。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/forecasts-analysis/chinas-industrial-economy-faces-growth-challenges-study-finds-10523303/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>中国的“世界工厂”经济模式面临着巨大的挑战</b></a> | 尽管中国经济在第二季度实现了 6.7% 的增长，超过了预期。长江商学院的一份研究指出，中国的“世界工厂”经济模式面临着巨大的挑战。该报告调研了超过 2000 个中国制造工厂，在 2016 年第二季度，超过 60% 的工厂生产过剩，供大于求。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>周杰伦和余文乐共同演绎 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/phantaci-x-madness-lookbook-staring-jay-chou-shawn-yue\" rel=\"nofollow\">PHANTACi 与 MADNESS 联名系列</a>。这也是双方在《头文字 D》之后，阔别十年的再度合作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231427mTIGOWA6fzRVLQiu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231428jxFEcy8rn6KlM5B0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231438LYjaKViSl0IAfysH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231451LnYhT5ObSg9EG43V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">成立于 2002 年的 rag &amp; bone 与日本著名包袋品牌 Porter 再度合作，带来了 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/rag-bone-x-porter-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">2016 秋冬系列</a>。这两款名为 Ruchsack 及 Gym Bag 的包，售价分别为 591 美元和 473 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231550yn1u5jrqiGpdTDKg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231605iZ1oCY5BGIwxhfsM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231615L9ikMmDtAqO6drH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231623si9AdWFbuzHJa8UO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231713vfKCPWOAbxTp28NS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/air-jordan-12-retro-gs-plum-fog\" rel=\"nofollow\">Air Jordan 12 Retro 推出女生专属的全新配色 Plum Fog</a>。皮革打造的白色鞋身配以粉紫色的外底，并搭配两颗金色的鞋带扣，时尚感十足。这款鞋将于 9 月 10 日正式上架，售价为 160 美元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609072317373Ku7eyT1x89GVOom.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231749uDqr15stWiZkw9KU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/2020-tokyo-olympics-comic-character-collaboration\" rel=\"nofollow\">2020 东京奥运推出多款动漫人物应援商品系列</a>。其中包括了 《美少女战士》、《蜡笔小新》、《One Piece》、《铁臂阿童木》、《火影忍者》、《龙珠》、《妖怪手表》以及《美少女战士》等八组动漫人物角色。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609072316557glus9aXbSNKQPpe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231919HVv3sxRT2rt8K76a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231926gjvinsV1kyPEo4H6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016090723193272nStkbCB8h5p4qw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231938IUceGkBflu0oKWwj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>意大利老牌时装品牌 Missoni 与 Converse 合作推出 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/missoni-x-converse-2016-chuck-taylor-all-star\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chuck Taylor All Star 系列</a>。融合了来自 Missoni 精湛的民族纺织工艺与 Converse 的街头美学。该系列已于 Converse 官网发售，定价为 150 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231021gZEqo1MvG2PsaB7h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231033YqlCK31ZvUgIFRjX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907231033Tw9Wz7XIUBsNrLdi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160908072415nNdajPSFlpWy0ws4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160908072415CUEyIsSk8Fd2P1jT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160908072435jkRqV7s0EPUKlA9L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/visvim-2016-fall-winter-leather-goods\" rel=\"nofollow\">visvim 人气款双折钱包再度回归</a>。2016 秋冬高调推出的这两款钱包都使用了拉链版本的标准款式，采用高档的牛皮制作，有金棕色和象牙白两种颜色，细节处有 visvim 的字样点缀。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907232012B6xwqYi3CIdtL8FQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609072320078GscIyqj6ZhArk0o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609072320383P5bna9RY4zNxwJC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907232024TQV03pzX6iHwBKPU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}